-- Dr. Manuel Bratos - English-Speaking Dental Clinic
('Dr. Manuel Bratos - Clínica Dental Bratos', 'Dental', 'English-speaking dental clinic in Madrid led by Dr. Manuel Bratos, a Certified Dental Technician (CDT) with international experience. Dr. Bratos worked as an adjunct assistant professor and researcher at Washington University of Seattle for three years, and continues to publish articles in the international scientific journal "Journal of Prosthetic Dentistry." Third-generation family dental clinic with over 40 years of experience. Specialists in dental implants, prosthodontics, orthodontics, pediatric dentistry, and treating patients with special needs. Award-winning research by the American Academy of Fixed Prosthodontics (AAFP), The Academy of Prosthodontics (AP), and Washington University. Fully English-speaking staff experienced with international patients and expats.', 'Avenida El Ferrol 18, 1º-4', 'Madrid', 'Madrid', '+34 913 233 380', NULL, 'https://clinicadentalbratos.es/', true, true, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
